  <brief_title>Irbesartan in Chinese Hypertensive Diabetics With Microalbuminuria</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study of Irbesartan 150mg Verses 300mg in Chinese Hypertensive Patients With Diabetes and Microalbuminuria</official_title>
  <sponsors>
