  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Primary objective:

        -  To determine if irbesartan 300mg is better than 150mg in protecting the kidneys in
           hypertensive patients with diabetes and microalbuminuria.

      Secondary objectives:

        -  To determine how well irbesartan 300mg is tolerated versus 150mg

        -  To determine the percentage of patients reaching the blood pressure target of 130/80
           mmHg
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
