  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Hypertensive patients, treated or untreated, with type 2 diabetes and urinary albumin
             excretion rate 20-200ug/min.

          -  Blood pressure of &lt; 180/110mmHg at baseline

          -  Normal serum creatinine

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Type 1 diabetes

          -  Use of angiotensin converting enzyme inhibitors or angiotensin receptor blockers in
             the 5 weeks before recruitment

          -  Pregnant or lactating women

          -  Severe hypertension

          -  Overt nephropathy

          -  Allergy to study drug

        The above information is not intended to contain all considerations relevant to a patient's
        potential participation in a clinical trial.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
